<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>AI Crime Intelligence Report</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            margin: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #1a365d;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #1a365d;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .header p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        .section h2 {
            color: #2563eb;
            margin-top: 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #cbd5e1;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .risk-high {
            color: #dc2626;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        th, td {
            text-align: left;
            padding: 8px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            color: #334155;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-top: 50px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <h1>Karnataka Police</h1>
        <h2>AI Crime Intelligence Report</h2>
        <p>Generated on: <%= date %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Overview</h2>
        <table>
            <tr>
                <th>FIR ID</th>
                <td><%= firData.id || 'N/A' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>District</th>
                <td><%= firData.district || 'N/A' %></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>Crime Type</th>
                <td><%= firData.crime_type || 'N/A' %></td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. AI Intelligence Analysis</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Unusual Activity:</strong> <%= analysis.unusual_activity_detected ? 'Detected' : 'None' %></li>
            <li><strong>Repeat Offenders:</strong> <%= (analysis.repeat_offenders_identified || []).join(', ') || 'None identified' %></li>
            <li><strong>Network Links:</strong> <%= (analysis.network_links || []).join(', ') || 'No known affiliations' %></li>
            <li><strong>Historical Match:</strong> <%= analysis.historical_trend_match || 'No significant match' %></li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Risk & Escalation (QuickML)</h2>
        <p>
            <strong>Risk Score:</strong> <span class="<%= prediction.risk_score > 70 ? 'risk-high' : '' %>"><%= prediction.risk_score || 0 %>/100</span><br>
            <strong>Escalation Probability:</strong> <%= (prediction.escalation_probability * 100) || 0 %>%
        </p>
        <p><em><%= prediction.prediction || prediction.details %></em></p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Actionable Summary & Deployment</h2>
        <p><%= summary %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        CONFIDENTIAL - This intelligence report was automatically generated by the AI Crime Intelligence Agent.<br>
        Unauthorized distribution is strictly prohibited.
    </div>

</body>
</html>
